cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DS, cs.SI 

This paper presents a method for semi-supervised learning using density-based distances, which is a common topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The method is also applicable to computer vision tasks (cs.CV) and involves graph-based algorithms (cs.DS). Additionally, the paper discusses a novel algorithm for efficient computation, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SI).
